<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chameleon-x" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(418890); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=418890&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571126" alt="Chameleon X" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=418890)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chameleon-x" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(418890); return false;">Chameleon X</a></span><br />
<strong>原文：</strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/exploration-log-a009-1">A009-1原文</a><br />
<strong>译者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/albus610" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5103825); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5103825&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571126" alt="Albus610" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5103825)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/albus610" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5103825); return false;">Albus610</a></span></p>
